<p class="t1"><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;">Mar&ccedil;o/2025</span></p>
</td>
<td style="text-align: center;" valign="top" width="305">
<p class="t1"><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;">7,71%</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
